**Description:**
Provides a dual-view system for the "Work" section. Users can toggle between "Visual Mode" (The Poetic: Big Images) and "Index Mode" (The Systematic: Raw Data Table).

**Context:**
This proves the agency is rooted in Data Science. It exposes the database structure behind the beauty.

**File Strategy:**
